data.description: Around the corner from the finest schools and a stroll to shops, restaurants & City train, this beautiful updated Pre-War slate-capped English Stone Colonial with 3-car garage has outstanding privacy laced by blooming gardens, majestic evergreens, flowering trees, rolling lawn and a sunny blue stone terrace.  Updated in 2013, the 12-room house has traditionally scaled rooms, multiple exposure garden views, romantic archways, living room with antique stone fireplace, bright formal dining room, eat-in kitchen, wine cellar, sauna and six bedrooms including private master.
